# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-15 14:26

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:20
translate chinese tammy16_39bb639d:

    # tm "Oh hey, [pcname]!"
    tm "嗨，[pcname]！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:22
translate chinese tammy16_c7aa7331:

    # tm "I wanted to let you know that I got another fight!"
    tm "想告诉你，我又有一场比赛了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:23
translate chinese tammy16_46fcf508:

    # pc "Oh yeah? Awesome!"
    pc "哦，是吗？太棒了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:25
translate chinese tammy16_537005d0:

    # tm "Yeah! I mean, it's the same opponent. Sara Death."
    tm "对！不过对手还是那个——莎拉·死亡。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:26
translate chinese tammy16_ff4ca977:

    # tm "They couldn't find anybody else to fight me around here."
    tm "这附近根本找不到其他人跟我打。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:27
translate chinese tammy16_c040e3a2:

    # pc "Still. A rematch! That'll be fun."
    pc "不管怎样，复赛！肯定很有趣。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:29
translate chinese tammy16_65a45e79:

    # tm "Yeah, so it's Friday evening. You're going to come, right?"
    tm "是啊，就在周五晚上。你会来吧？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:30
translate chinese tammy16_a248948f:

    # pc "Of course."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:31
translate chinese tammy16_0d0b0b78:

    # tm "Good. Suzy's coming to this one too."
    tm "太好了。苏茜这次也会来。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:33
translate chinese tammy16_a716e406:

    # tm "I'm so fucking excited!"
    tm "我简直兴奋得要命！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:34
translate chinese tammy16_c03b2498:

    # tm "Ready to work out?"
    tm "准备好去练了？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:35
translate chinese tammy16_81e72625:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do it!"
    pc "嗯，走吧！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:46
translate chinese tammy16b_d3127e62:

    # "Tonight is Tammy's fight. I better head over to the gym to support her."
    "今晚是塔米的比赛。我得去健身房支持她。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:50
translate chinese tammy16b_fc7a2349:

    # "The place is packed tonight. Even more people than the first fight. I guess everybody wants to see the rematch."
    "今晚场内人满为患。比第一场比赛时还要多。看来大家都想看这场复赛。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:51
translate chinese tammy16b_c1a9fded:

    # "I spot Tammy and Suzy hanging out near the ring and walk over to them."
    "我看到塔米和苏茜在擂台附近闲逛，便走过去找她们。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:54
translate chinese tammy16b_ef965655:

    # tm "Hey, [pcname]. You in my corner again?"
    tm "嘿，[pcname]。你又在我角落里啦？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:55
translate chinese tammy16b_351f8f78:

    # pc "I'm always in your corner, girl."
    pc "我一直都在你这边，姑娘。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:58
translate chinese tammy16b_7de5fb0a:

    # tm "I know you are. Love you!"
    tm "我知道的。爱你！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:59
translate chinese tammy16b_ce2ae2bf:

    # pc "Love you too."
    pc "我也爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:60
translate chinese tammy16b_fbdb8489:

    # "Chuck, the gym owner and referee, steps onto the stage and speaks into a microphone."
    "健身房老板兼裁判查克走上台，对着麦克风说道。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:61
translate chinese tammy16b_03a792fe:

    # "Chuck" "All right, everybody. Fighters to the ring."
    "Chuck" "好了，各位。选手请上擂台。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:64
translate chinese tammy16b_bc20373a:

    # tm "Guess I gotta go. Wish me luck."
    tm "我得去啦。祝我好运。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:65
translate chinese tammy16b_70969e05:

    # ss "You don't need it. You're going to wipe the mat with her."
    ss "你不需要。你肯定会把她打得落花流水。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:66
translate chinese tammy16b_8407fcdb:

    # pc "You trained so hard. You're a beast."
    pc "你练得那么刻苦。你简直是个猛兽。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:67
translate chinese tammy16b_0fc82d62:

    # tm "Thanks, guys."
    tm "谢谢你们。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:70
translate chinese tammy16b_4d3281d1:

    # ss "You better get up there in her corner. She needs you."
    ss "你最好去她的角落里。她需要你。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:71
translate chinese tammy16b_2cda7690:

    # pc "You don't want to?"
    pc "你不愿意去吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:72
translate chinese tammy16b_2475c65e:

    # ss "No, I'm going to go cheer from the back. I don't like to see her get hit."
    ss "不，我要在后面加油。我不喜欢看她挨打。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:73
translate chinese tammy16b_7ebf9a37:

    # ss "But you'll hear me, I'm sure."
    ss "但你肯定能听到我的声音。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:76
translate chinese tammy16b_8ba7b5ed:

    # "I climb up into Tammy's corner as Chuck introduces the fighters."
    "当查克介绍选手时，我爬进了塔米的角落。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:77
translate chinese tammy16b_263516ea:

    # "Sara Death looks somehow even bigger and more jacked than she did last time they fought."
    "萨拉·死亡看起来比上次交手时更加高大壮硕。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:78
translate chinese tammy16b_dd7b01f4:

    # "Tammy is so much smaller it's sometimes hard to believe that she can take an opponent like that down."
    "塔米身材如此娇小，有时真让人难以相信她能击倒这样的对手。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:79
translate chinese tammy16b_edae56fc:

    # "Chuck" "... Our return opponent in this rematch, Sara Death!"
    "Chuck" "……本次复赛中我们的回归对手，萨拉·死亡！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:83
translate chinese tammy16b_a31e4957:

    # "Chuck" "And in this corner, undefeated so far in her amateur fighting career and hoping to continue that streak tonight..."
    "Chuck" "而在这个角落，一位在业余格斗生涯中至今保持不败、并希望今晚延续这一纪录的选手……"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:85
translate chinese tammy16b_83b35d9b:

    # "Chuck" "And in this corner, looking to get revenge on the beating she took last fight..."
    "Chuck" "而在这一角，渴望为上一场比赛的惨败复仇的是……"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:86
translate chinese tammy16b_96ba703d:

    # "Chuck" "... standing five-foot-six-inches tall and weighing in at 130 pounds..."
    "Chuck" "……身高五英尺六英寸，体重130磅……"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:87
translate chinese tammy16b_ec4b18ff:

    # "Chuck" "Tammy \"Wham! Bam!\" Zamora!"
    "Chuck" "塔米·“砰！啪！”·萨莫拉！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:90
translate chinese tammy16b_6f4f75f7:

    # "Chuck takes them to the middle of the ring and goes over the rules with them."
    "查克将她们带到擂台中央，向她们讲解比赛规则。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:91
translate chinese tammy16b_0b6f40cb:

    # "Sara smiles the whole time. I can see Sara and Tammy muttering something to each other and laughing."
    "萨拉全程都在微笑。我看到萨拉和塔米互相低语着什么，还咯咯地笑。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:92
translate chinese tammy16b_24d8b054:

    # "Even though they're about to beat the crap out of each other, it seems like they're having a good time."
    "尽管她们马上就要把对方打得落花流水，但看起来她们似乎玩得很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:93
translate chinese tammy16b_1b6ae11e:

    # "When they're done, they touch gloves and return to their corners."
    "讲解完毕后，两人碰了碰拳套，各自回到自己的角落。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:96
translate chinese tammy16b_fcfdafdf:

    # pc "You got this."
    pc "你行。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:97
translate chinese tammy16b_3caaf546:

    # tm "You're goddamn right."
    tm "那还用说。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:98
translate chinese tammy16b_0929120c:

    # "Chuck" "Three... Two... One... FIGHT!"
    "Chuck" "三……二……一……开打！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:101
translate chinese tammy16b_ec9b5571:

    # "They both rush to the middle of the ring and the crowd goes wild."
    "两人冲向擂台中央，全场观众瞬间沸腾。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:104
translate chinese tammy16b_679f2669:

    # "Even over the yells of all of those around me, I can hear Suzy in the back, cheering loudly for our girlfriend."
    "即便周围人声鼎沸，我仍能听见后台苏茜为我们女朋友大声呐喊助威。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:107
translate chinese tammy16b_647f4a54:

    # "They circle around each other a bit, testing out their range, looking for openings."
    "她们绕着对方转了几圈，试探距离，寻找破绽。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:110
translate chinese tammy16b_5d7efc88:

    # "Tammy is trying to stay loose, moving in and out quickly to land leg kicks."
    "塔米试图保持灵活，快速进退，试图踢中对方腿部。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:111
translate chinese tammy16b_e3d4107b:

    # "She knows that getting too close would mean that she could be taken down to the ground."
    "她深知若靠得太近，很可能被对手撂倒在地。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:112
translate chinese tammy16b_a88a4b4f:

    # "Having the much larger Sara on top of her could easily lead to her getting overwhelmed."
    "若让体型庞大的莎拉压在身下，她极易陷入被动。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:115
translate chinese tammy16b_a3883dc3:

    # "Of course, taking one of those big fists on her chin could knock her down as well."
    "当然，若下巴被那只巨拳击中，同样会让她倒地。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:116
translate chinese tammy16b_b3da4826:

    # "Every second she's in this fight, there's more of a chance of her getting hit and knocked out."
    "在这场对决中，每一秒都意味着她被击中并被KO的几率在增加。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:119
translate chinese tammy16b_cdd3604c:

    # "Tammy is able to land a few good hits, but Sara just takes them and keeps coming."
    "塔米虽然成功击中了几记重拳，但莎拉只是硬扛着继续进攻。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:122
translate chinese tammy16b_248b11e5:

    # "Then the referee calls the end of the round and steps in to separate them back to their corners."
    "随后裁判宣布本回合结束，上前将两人分开，送回各自的角落。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:125
translate chinese tammy16b_5dca43c0:

    # tm "How am I looking out there?"
    tm "我在那里的表现怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:126
translate chinese tammy16b_40609e22:

    # pc "You look great. Really fucking sexy."
    pc "你表现得棒极了。真的他妈的性感。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:127
translate chinese tammy16b_4586870d:

    # tm "Haha, I need a real coach."
    tm "哈哈，我需要一个真正的教练。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:128
translate chinese tammy16b_4e5ec89e:

    # pc "Seriously, you're looking good. Moving fast. Staying on your toes."
    pc "说真的，你表现得很不错。移动迅速，始终保持警觉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:129
translate chinese tammy16b_eafbc9cd:

    # pc "I liked those leg kicks. They seemed to slow her down a bit. Her being slow is good. You can take advantage of that."
    pc "我喜欢那些腿踢。似乎让她慢了一点。她变慢了是好事。你可以利用这一点。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:130
translate chinese tammy16b_2d3b068d:

    # pc "Just be careful about her taking you down."
    pc "只是要小心她把你撂倒。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:131
translate chinese tammy16b_ec4282cb:

    # tm "Yeah, that's what I'm scared of. I've never been on the ground with her before."
    tm "是啊，这就是我担心的。我以前从来没和她在地上缠斗过。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:132
translate chinese tammy16b_6ef7cd76:

    # pc "You got this. I'm pretty sure you won that first round. Just keep moving and stay hard to hit."
    pc "你没问题的。我敢肯定你赢了第一回合。只要继续移动，保持难以击中。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:133
translate chinese tammy16b_850254f5:

    # tm "You got it. Thanks, coach."
    tm "明白了。谢谢，教练。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:136
translate chinese tammy16b_2221ccc4:

    # "When the bell rings, they're right back in the middle of the ring again, trading punches."
    "铃声一响，两人立刻回到擂台中央，拳脚交锋。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:137
translate chinese tammy16b_c6a976b0:

    # "Tammy is able to block most of Sara's punches and sneak in a few of her own."
    "塔米成功挡住了莎拉的大部分拳击，并趁机还击了几次。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:140
translate chinese tammy16b_9dbf1b1c:

    # "Then Tammy hops back and gets another hard kick to Sara's leg, the slap of shin on thigh echoing through the gym."
    "随后塔米向后跳起，又一记重踢击中莎拉的腿部，小腿撞击大腿的声响在健身房里回荡。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:141
translate chinese tammy16b_4c60ba4c:

    # "Sara winces. That one hurt."
    "莎拉皱起眉头。这一脚真疼。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:144
translate chinese tammy16b_e41ad8f5:

    # "The pain and the frustration gets to Sara then and she growls in anger as she charges forward."
    "疼痛与挫败感瞬间涌上心头，莎拉怒吼着向前冲去。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:145
translate chinese tammy16b_03576045:

    # "She's throwing haymakers now, backing Tammy up towards the ropes."
    "她现在挥出重拳，将塔米逼向绳边。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:146
translate chinese tammy16b_028976a4:

    # "Sara has lost all defense in this moment. If Tammy could take advantage of it, she might be able to end the fight."
    "此刻莎拉已完全放弃防守。如果塔米能抓住这个机会，或许就能结束比赛。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:149
translate chinese tammy16b_5dc11d33:

    # "But then one of the punches connects, cracking against Tammy's jaw and rolling her eyes back."
    "但随后一记重拳正中塔米的下巴，她眼珠一翻，倒在了垫子上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:150
translate chinese tammy16b_ade70eed:

    # "I hear Suzy in the back cry out in shock as Tammy falls to the mat."
    "我听到后排的苏西惊呼出声，塔米倒在了垫子上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:153
translate chinese tammy16b_76769a9d:

    # "At first, I think that's it, that Tammy is knocked out, but she quickly shakes her head and starts fighting back."
    "起初，我以为比赛结束了，以为塔米被击倒了，但她迅速摇了摇头，开始反击。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:154
translate chinese tammy16b_8cf6bab3:

    # "But now Sara is on top of her, raining punches down onto her."
    "但此刻莎拉已压在她身上，拳头如雨点般砸向她。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:155
translate chinese tammy16b_f5522b72:

    # "Chuck is close and I can tell he's about to stop the fight."
    "查克就在附近，我看得出他正准备终止比赛。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:158
translate chinese tammy16b_12ebb29b:

    # "What happens next is so fast that I can barely follow it."
    "接下来的事情发生得太快，我几乎跟不上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:159
translate chinese tammy16b_a46fd698:

    # "Tammy grabs Sara's wrist and bucks her hips, moving her legs up towards Sara's head."
    "塔米抓住莎拉的手腕，猛地扭动腰部，双腿向上蹬向莎拉的头部。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:162
translate chinese tammy16b_14e97ff6:

    # "Then Tammy rotates and has Sara's arm fully stretched out."
    "接着塔米一记旋转，将莎拉的手臂彻底拉直。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:163
translate chinese tammy16b_ca12b0e7:

    # "Sara cries out in pain. If she doesn't tap soon, Tammy could easily break her arm."
    "莎拉痛得大叫。如果她不赶紧拍垫认输，塔米随时可能把她的胳膊折断。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:166
translate chinese tammy16b_f3df8ee4:

    # "She reluctantly taps and the crowd goes insane."
    "她不情愿地拍了拍垫子，全场顿时沸腾。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:169
translate chinese tammy16b_2d3791c3:

    # "I can't hear anything, the room is so loud and suddenly Suzy is right there, jumping up onto my shoulder."
    "我什么都听不见，整个房间嘈杂得要命，突然苏茜就扑了过来，跳到我肩上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:170
translate chinese tammy16b_be32fa84:

    # "I hold her high while she cheers."
    "我高高举起她，任她欢呼雀跃。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:173
translate chinese tammy16b_411f816b:

    # "Chuck announces the winner, but it's impossible to hear him over the roaring crowd."
    "查克宣布了胜者，但喧嚣的人群声盖过了他的声音，根本听不清。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:174
translate chinese tammy16b_67d97e00:

    # "Tammy and Sara are both crying in the ring. Suzy's crying on my shoulder. Hell, I'm crying a little bit too."
    "塔米和莎拉都在擂台上哭泣。苏茜在我肩头哭泣。见鬼，我也不禁流下了一两滴眼泪。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:177
translate chinese tammy16b_09e2a5ca:

    # "Then Tammy runs over and kisses Suzy."
    "接着塔米跑过来亲了亲苏茜。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:178
translate chinese tammy16b_5354153a:

    # ss "You're a fucking queen! I love you!"
    ss "“你真是个他妈的女王！我爱你！”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:179
translate chinese tammy16b_4039bf0e:

    # tm "I love both of you so fucking much!"
    tm "我他妈的太爱你们两个了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:182
translate chinese tammy16b_c191fa62:

    # "The next half hour passes by in a blur as everybody congratulates Tammy and wants to talk to her and Sara."
    "接下来的半小时恍如隔世，大家纷纷向塔米道贺，都想和她还有萨拉聊上几句。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:183
